uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model

Class DConcept<D extends DObject>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model.DConcept<D>

  • public class DConcept<D extends DObject>
extends java.lang.Object
    Type-safe representation of a concept-level frame within the Object Model (OM). Combines a reference to an OM class that defines a general type for the represented concept, with a concept-level frame representing the actual concept. The frame must be subsumed by the frame to which the OM class is bound.

    NOTE: A concept-level frame that has multiple ancestors that are bound to OM classes can give rise to multiple distinct DConcept objects, each pairing the frame with a different OM class.
